------------------------------------------------------------------------
r3989 | coekie | 2005-09-10 03:23:27 +0000 (Sat, 10 Sep 2005) | 3 lines
Changed paths:
   M /irssi/trunk/src/fe-common/irc/fe-whois.c

with unknown (special) lines in whois, display the full content, not just the first parameter
