r2448 | cras | 2002-02-15 13:38:24 +0000 (Fri, 15 Feb 2002) | 6 lines
Changed paths:
   M /irssi/trunk/configure.in
   M /irssi/trunk/src/fe-text/gui-entry.c
   M /irssi/trunk/src/fe-text/gui-entry.h
   M /irssi/trunk/src/fe-text/gui-expandos.c
