r2388 | cras | 2002-02-04 04:27:45 +0000 (Mon, 04 Feb 2002) | 7 lines
Changed paths:
   M /irssi/trunk/src/core/log.c
   M /irssi/trunk/src/core/log.h
   M /irssi/trunk/src/fe-common/core/fe-log.c
