------------------------------------------------------------------------
r2243 | cras | 2001-12-14 01:54:12 +0000 (Fri, 14 Dec 2001) | 6 lines
Changed paths:
   M /irssi/trunk/src/core/commands.c
   M /irssi/trunk/src/core/server-rec.h
   M /irssi/trunk/src/core/servers.c
