r1228 | cras | 2001-02-17 10:35:35 +0000 (Sat, 17 Feb 2001) | 7 lines
Changed paths:
   M /irssi/trunk/configure.in
   M /irssi/trunk/src/core/modules.c
   M /irssi/trunk/src/core/modules.h
