r1139 | cras | 2001-01-21 04:14:24 +0000 (Sun, 21 Jan 2001) | 6 lines
Changed paths:
   M /irssi/trunk/src/fe-common/core/fe-messages.c
   M /irssi/trunk/src/fe-common/core/formats.c
